id":"0fc4f53bbbc89b68fed26fa58934f8d5b4da1f69","tid":2035083,"uid":71770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"唔取消其實冇乜所謂?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"唔取消如果你係支那香港澳門有事外國大使管幫唔到你，任支那魚肉"},{"pid":"dd430a68aaf18f1b15ae81b301da6d27ba20df35","tid":2035083,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=d1341a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"a55897cc9b8f15c45154ce4c0107b6b87db164cf","tid":2035083,"uid":71770,"like":0,"dislike":0,